*CB01] ▷ The Conjuring: Il rito finale Fi𝚕m inte𝚛o St𝚛eam𝚒ng ITA [2025] in Al𝚝a Def𝚒nizi𝚘ne

Reads a JSON file: audit-report.json from C:/Users/{userprofile}/Desktop/audit-log-report as raw text.  Parses the JSON into a PowerShell object with ConvertFrom-Json.  Flattens all advisories: iterates $data.advisories property values into a list (note: name says “critical” but there’s no actual severity filter yet).  Expands findings: for each advisory → for each finding → builds a [PSCustomObject] with key fields (AdvisoryId, Title, Severity, ModuleName, Versions, Recommendation, URL, and joined paths).  De-dupes/sorts results by AdvisoryId with Sort-Object -Unique.  Ensures output folder exists at C:/Users/{userprofile}/Desktop/audit-log-report; creates it if missing.  Exports the dataset to Excel (all-audit-report.xlsx) using Export-Excel with auto-sizing and worksheet name ALL Advisories.  Resolves the full file path and prints a success message with the Excel file location.
